# Astronaut Health Simulation Engine (AHSE)

A lightweight, modular simulation engine to model astronaut physiological changes under mission parameters.

## Quickstart

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m ahse.cli run --config examples/sample_mission.json --out results/
```
